// PublicBanner Overall page banner derived from visible monitor statuses (PRD-004 4).
type PublicBanner string

// PublicDisplayedMonitor Public-safe projection of one displayed monitor (PRD-004 3.6 left column). Carries ONLY the friendly name, public status, uptime, and history; it never carries the raw url, method, headers, body, assertions, or failure detail.
